<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٤- <span style="color:#008000">(أخبرنا)</span> : مَالِكٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> عن زَيدِ بنِ أسْلَم:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98">أَنَّ رسولَ اللَّه صلى الَّله عليه وسلم قَالَ:</span> <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَنْ غَيَّرَ دِينَهُ فاضْرِبُوا عُنُقَهُ»</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>